#include <bits/stdc++.h>

using namespace std;

map <int,int> d;
map <string,int> x;

void init()
{
d[1]=31;
x["JAN"]=1;
d[2]=28;
x["FEB"]=2;
d[3]=31;
x["MAR"]=3;
d[4]=30;
x["APR"]=4;
d[5]=31;
x["MAY"]=5;
d[6]=30;
x["JUN"]=6;
d[7]=31;
x["JUL"]=7;
d[8]=31;
x["AUG"]=8;
d[9]=30;
x["SEP"]=9;
d[10]=31;
x["OCT"]=10;
d[11]=30;
x["NOV"]=11;
d[12]=31;
x["DEC"]=12;
}

int main()
{
    int t,j;
    scanf("%d",&t);
    for(j=1;j<=t;j++)
    {
    int i,day,year,s=0;
    string date,month;
    cin>>date;
    init();
    day=((int)(date[0]-'0')*10)+(int(date[1]-'0'));
    month=date.substr(3,3);
    year=((int)(date[7]-'0')*1000)+((int)(date[8]-'0')*100)+((int)(date[9]-'0')*10)+((int)(date[10]-'0'));
    if(year%400==0||(year%4==0&&year%100!=0))
    {
        d[2]=29;
    }
    for(i=1;i<x[month];i++)
    {
        s+=d[i];
    }
    s+=day;
    printf("Case %d: ",j);
    if(s<=300)
    {
        cout<<s<<" Hundreds";
    }
    else
    if(s-300<=60)
    {
        s-=300;
        cout<<s<<" Tens";
    }
    else
    {
        s-=360;
        cout<<s<<" Ones";
    }
    printf("\n");
    }
    return 0;
}
